===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌntʃ|-ʌntʃ]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-es}}

#A [[meal]] eaten later in the day than [[breakfast]] and earlier than [[lunch]], replacing both meals, and often consisting of some foods that would normally be eaten at breakfast and some foods that would normally be eaten at lunch.

